text: Andres Dellatorre (born 9 July 1980) is an Argentine tennis player. Dellatorre has a career high ATP singles ranking of 210 achieved on 6 October 2003. He also has a career high doubles ranking of 209 achieved on 10 January 2005. Dellatorre has won 1 ATP Challenger doubles title at the 2004 Tampere Open. ==Tour titles== {| class=wikitable |- !
